00:11:34,760 --> 00:11:36,440
(Pikirkanlah para pejabat tua.)

208
00:11:37,480 --> 00:11:39,640
(Berapa besar pengorbanan kami)

209
00:11:39,840 --> 00:11:42,240
(baru bisa mengganti kelangsungan hidupmu.)

210
00:11:43,880 --> 00:11:44,800
(Baginda,)

211
00:11:45,880 --> 00:11:48,880
(kau adalah harapan terakhir kami.)

